<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 10:07:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于援助遥不可及，加沙儿童的营养不良状况不断蔓延</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-aid-waiting-beyond-their-reach-malnutrition-among-gazas-children-keeps-spreading/0000018e-56c7-daff-a9ce-feef835a0000</link><description>海上援助走廊受到广泛关注，但加沙组织表示，陆路供应对于满足紧急人道主义需求至关重要。联合国记录了 16 起援助车队枪击事件，组织认为大多数事件都是以色列军队幕后黑手</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 08:15:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-aid-waiting-beyond-their-reach-malnutrition-among-gazas-children-keeps-spreading/0000018e-56c7-daff-a9ce-feef835a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的利库德集团无法解开萨尔之谜，但他们无论如何都希望他回来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-likud-cant-unravel-the-saar-riddle-but-they-want-him-back-anyway/0000018e-5916-d88e-a39e-7db71ed60000</link><description>吉迪恩·萨尔坚持加入的战时内阁的紧张局势已达到沸点，与本尼·甘茨的冲突似乎迫在眉睫。一位利库德集团部长在谈到这位前以色列国防军司令时表示，“他太亲美了，他已经成为一个烦恼”</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 04:01:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-likud-cant-unravel-the-saar-riddle-but-they-want-him-back-anyway/0000018e-5916-d88e-a39e-7db71ed60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队：90名哈马斯恐怖分子在加沙Al-Shifa医院被打死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article-live/gaza-officials-at-least-15-killed-in-airstrike-u-s-deeply-worried-over-famine-report/0000018e-59ae-d5db-abdf-59fee1930000</link><description>抗议者封锁以色列主要高速公路，呼吁释放人质 ■ 卫生官员称，针对加沙中部努塞拉特难民营房屋的空袭造成至少 15 人死亡 ■ 联合国人权事务高级专员表示，以色列在加沙的行动“可能相当于使用■ 外交部长表示，加拿大将停止向以色列提供武器 ​​■ 两名辛贝特特工在约旦河西岸袭击中受伤，袭击者身亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 02:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article-live/gaza-officials-at-least-15-killed-in-airstrike-u-s-deeply-worried-over-famine-report/0000018e-59ae-d5db-abdf-59fee1930000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡考虑创造性解决方案，将萨尔带入战时内阁，同时将本格维尔排除在外</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-mulls-creative-solution-to-bring-saar-into-war-cabinet-keep-ben-gvir-out/0000018e-5900-d4f6-a9be-d92aa9470000</link><description>总理计划给予吉迪恩·萨尔在战时内阁中的观察员地位，并正在考虑让他成为“定期受邀者”，但极右翼国家安全部长本·格维尔表示，他将要求与萨尔同等的地位</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:35:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-mulls-creative-solution-to-bring-saar-into-war-cabinet-keep-ben-gvir-out/0000018e-5900-d4f6-a9be-d92aa9470000</guid></item><item><title>AG 坚称，以色列允许警察使用间谍软件的新法律必须涵盖腐败案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-law-allowing-police-to-use-spyware-must-cover-corruption-cases-ag-insists/0000018e-58ef-d5db-abdf-58ff8b740000</link><description>司法部长告诉 Itamar Ben-Gvir，她不能支持批准仅适用于涉嫌严重犯罪案件的间谍软件监视的法律</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:15:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-law-allowing-police-to-use-spyware-must-cover-corruption-cases-ag-insists/0000018e-58ef-d5db-abdf-58ff8b740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长谴责加拿大外长停止向以色列运送武器的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/report-canada-will-stop-sending-arms-to-israel-foreign-minister-says/0000018e-58a9-d88e-a39e-7dbb83210000</link><description>以色列外交部长表示：“历史将对加拿大当前的行为做出严厉的评价。”加拿大的声明凸显了对以色列在加沙行动的批评越来越多，因为西方国家发现自己因向以色列出售武器而陷入困境</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 21:42:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/report-canada-will-stop-sending-arms-to-israel-foreign-minister-says/0000018e-58a9-d88e-a39e-7dbb83210000</guid></item><item><title>两名辛贝特特工在约旦河西岸枪击事件中受伤；巴勒斯坦人在另一起事件中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/two-shin-bet-agents-wounded-in-west-bank-attack-palestinian-killed-in-separate-incident/0000018e-581e-d7fb-a1df-d8fe78930000</link><description>来自杰宁的 30 岁袭击者向辛贝特特工开枪，被枪杀；消息人士称，在另一起事件中，一名 43 岁的巴勒斯坦人被犹太定居者枪杀。这一说法遭到以色列国防军消息人士反驳，他说该男子在袭击以色列国防军士兵后被杀死</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 20:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/two-shin-bet-agents-wounded-in-west-bank-attack-palestinian-killed-in-separate-incident/0000018e-581e-d7fb-a1df-d8fe78930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列确实存在哈斯巴拉问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-19/ty-article/.highlight/israel-really-does-have-a-hasbara-problem/0000018e-57e4-d9a8-a5ae-ffed63bf0000</link><description>如果在国际上还有人愿意为以色列挺身而出，他能说一口流利的英语，牢牢掌握美国的自由主义价值观，并且能够满足内塔尼亚胡严格的纯洁性测试——请他们站起来吗？在内塔尼亚胡发号施令时可能不会</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:54:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-19/ty-article/.highlight/israel-really-does-have-a-hasbara-problem/0000018e-57e4-d9a8-a5ae-ffed63bf0000</guid></item><item><title>贾里德·库什纳称加沙海滨财产“非常有价值”，建议以色列“将人们转移出去然后清理”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/jared-kushner-gaza-seaside-land-very-valuable-israel-must-move-people-out-clean-up/0000018e-57b3-d4f6-a9be-dfbb4ed30000</link><description>在接受哈佛大学采访时，特朗普的白宫高级顾问将潜在的巴勒斯坦国描述为“一个超级糟糕的主意”，并建议以色列“在内盖夫推土机”来安置流离失所的巴勒斯坦人，以便重建加沙并“完成工作”</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:11:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/jared-kushner-gaza-seaside-land-very-valuable-israel-must-move-people-out-clean-up/0000018e-57b3-d4f6-a9be-dfbb4ed30000</guid></item><item><title>你需要知道的，第 165 天：卡塔尔称拉法行动可能危及停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-165/0000018e-57c9-d9a8-a5ae-ffcd316f0000</link><description>拜登表示，他告诉内塔尼亚胡派团队前往华盛顿，讨论如何在不针对拉法行动的情况下针对哈马斯美国因涉嫌战争罪暂停向以色列转让武器 ■ 白宫对最近一份称加沙迫在眉睫的饥荒的报告“深表关切” ■ 战争结束 165 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 17:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-165/0000018e-57c9-d9a8-a5ae-ffcd316f0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔在与以色列摩萨德主席会谈后表示，拉法入侵可能导致加沙人质协议谈判破裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/rafah-invasion-risks-breakdown-of-negotiations-qatar-says-after-talks-with-mossad-chief/0000018e-5773-d5fc-adde-77ffbe3d0000</link><description>以色列代表团目前正在多哈参加另一轮人质交易和停火协议谈判，但以色列当局、人质家属和美国之间仍对协议条件和当前行动存在争议</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 17:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/rafah-invasion-risks-breakdown-of-negotiations-qatar-says-after-talks-with-mossad-chief/0000018e-5773-d5fc-adde-77ffbe3d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡告诉以色列议会：“我们必须团结起来反对”美国阻止以色列入侵拉法的企图</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-knesset-we-must-all-unite-against-u-s-effort-to-prevent-invasion-of-rafah/0000018e-5794-d4f6-a9be-dfbe4d070000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，总理告诉立法者，以色列“与美国对于是否需要进入拉法存在争议，但对于是否需要消灭哈马斯没有争议”</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 17:00:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-knesset-we-must-all-unite-against-u-s-effort-to-prevent-invasion-of-rafah/0000018e-5794-d4f6-a9be-dfbe4d070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名在希法医院附近的加沙战斗中丧生的预备役人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-reservist-killed-in-gaza-combat-near-al-shifa-hospital/0000018e-5726-d349-a9fe-df2f9e8b0000</link><description>塞巴斯蒂安·海昂准尉，51 岁，来自以色列中部罗什艾因，是一名以色列国防军预备役军人，在加沙地带希法医院附近的战斗中丧生。一名预备役军人说：“以色列国防军今天失去了一位罕见的战士”</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 15:07:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-reservist-killed-in-gaza-combat-near-al-shifa-hospital/0000018e-5726-d349-a9fe-df2f9e8b0000</guid></item><item><title>自10月7日以来我第一次访问，我看到以色列的灵魂逐渐被侵蚀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/etan-nechin-op-ed/0000018e-4cbb-d1ed-a7ef-5dbf26cf0000</link><description>我回到了一个仍然因恐怖和悲伤而瘫痪的社会，对加沙的苦难麻木不仁，其领导人煽动愤世嫉俗的民族主义 - 但我也看到了反抗的曙光</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 14:30:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/etan-nechin-op-ed/0000018e-4cbb-d1ed-a7ef-5dbf26cf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列旷日持久、漫无目的的战争是一张走向国际孤立的单程票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-lingering-aimless-war-is-a-one-way-ticket-to-international-isolation/0000018e-56a7-dce2-adaf-7feff9290000</link><description>加沙战争已经进行了五个多月，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡对战争可实现的目标一无所知，但坚决让战争的管理服从于他的政治生存。如果这种趋势继续下去，以色列将巩固其在世界舞台上被遗弃的地位</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 14:28:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-lingering-aimless-war-is-a-one-way-ticket-to-international-isolation/0000018e-56a7-dce2-adaf-7feff9290000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼国家安全部长庆祝自 10 月 7 日以来发放了 10 万张持枪许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-minister-celebrates-handing-out-100k-gun-permits-since-oct-7/0000018e-5682-dc6f-adff-df87a3ae0000</link><description>伊塔马尔·本·格维尔 (Itamar Ben Gvir) 表示，“在平民可以保护自己的地方，[10 月 7 日]灾难的严重程度没有那么严重。”他对武装以色列平民的宽松政策引起了广泛谴责</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:11:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-minister-celebrates-handing-out-100k-gun-permits-since-oct-7/0000018e-5682-dc6f-adff-df87a3ae0000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列专注于军事行动，哈马斯将继续实现其目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-will-continue-to-achieve-its-goals-if-israel-only-focuses-on-military-action/0000018e-566e-dc6f-adff-df6f4d730000</link><description>加沙战争实际上是社会战争，除非我们承认我们无法取得并维持成功</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:11:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-will-continue-to-achieve-its-goals-if-israel-only-focuses-on-military-action/0000018e-566e-dc6f-adff-df6f4d730000</guid></item><item><title>拜登所做的一切都无法罢免内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/nothing-biden-does-can-remove-netanyahu/0000018e-55e9-d5d7-abae-55ff2b800000</link><description>以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡无力承担 10 月 7 日事件的责任，也无意辞职。在他在议会中的竞争对手齐心协力之前，任何外部压力都不会让他下台</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:07:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/nothing-biden-does-can-remove-netanyahu/0000018e-55e9-d5d7-abae-55ff2b800000</guid></item><item><title>救护车延误和交通堵塞：自加沙战争开始以来，以色列军队封锁了进入西岸村庄的通道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/delayed-ambulances-and-long-trips-israeli-army-blocks-entry-to-west-bank-villages/0000018e-561a-d0e6-afbe-fe7e57a10000</link><description>一名志愿医务人员表示，“即使在紧急情况下，我们也无法通过检查站”，因为西岸巴勒斯坦居民报告说，自 10 月 7 日以来，他们必须使用危险的土路并通知定居点才能出行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 11:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/delayed-ambulances-and-long-trips-israeli-army-blocks-entry-to-west-bank-villages/0000018e-561a-d0e6-afbe-fe7e57a10000</guid></item><item><title>由于联盟关系紧张，赋予政府权力任命城市拉比的有争议法案被搁置</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/contentious-bill-giving-government-power-over-rabbi-posts-shelved-amid-coalition-tension/0000018e-555b-dfaa-af8e-d7dbccca0000</link><description>战时内阁部长本尼·甘茨表示，“我们必须围绕战争目标团结起来，不要参与会造成不和的有争议的立法”，各政治派别的立法者都对该法案的推迟表示欢迎</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 08:38:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/contentious-bill-giving-government-power-over-rabbi-posts-shelved-amid-coalition-tension/0000018e-555b-dfaa-af8e-d7dbccca0000</guid></item></channel></rss>